oney is fraud. The =E2=80=9Cpotentially valuable economic information=E2=80=
=9D theory looks to the Supreme Court too much like =E2=80=9Chonest service=
s,=E2=80=9D so it reversed the convictions. It seems to me like =E2=80=9Cwe=
 tricked the government into giving us a $750 million construction contract=
=E2=80=9D looks a lot like taking money from the government, but for some r=
